::section services "Services"
MusicService owns library state, selected track, playback state, player backend, volume, queue IDs, shuffle/repeat, playlists, lyrics, audio effects, subtitles, video state, streaming state, snapshots, and saved playback state.

MusicService => central library, track, playback, queue, shuffle/repeat, playlists, lyrics, effects, subtitles, video, streaming, snapshots, and resume state.
MusicScannerService => scans paths, reads Android hints, detects media, parses metadata, extracts covers, and creates Music objects.
ID3Parser => parses MP3, APE, MP4/M4A, FLAC, cover art, duration, and filename fallback metadata.
CoverExtractor => extracts cover art from local files or bundled assets.
CoverColorService => creates cover palettes and fallback colors.
YoutubeMusicService => search, download, stream, warm cache, resolve download directory, run helper code, and friendly errors.
LocalShareService => HTTP share server, discovery, manifest fetch, transfer, pause/resume/cancel, duplicate checks, safe filenames.
WifiDirectService => Android Wi-Fi Direct permissions, discovery, connection, disconnect, stop discovery, and trusted devices.
MusicBrainzTagService => MusicBrainz search, scoring, token normalization, and recording metadata.
PlayerAudioHandler => OS media controls, media buttons, timeline, metadata, Windows SMTC guard, and external playback state.
PerformancePolicy => animation, particles, blur, cache scale, and visual-cost decisions.
Responsive => viewport scaling and sizing helpers.
